Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second L, as well as the one I suspect to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. This is Takada Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Messages from Kira will now be transmitted as the law to the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can use Takada Kiyomi in this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove all bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun is... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun is... Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:57.01,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(367,330)}Ridicule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pieces are now in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this stage, {\alpha&HFF&}I should go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this stage, I should go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Lester.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come back to New York one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to Japan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will support you from New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why do you want me back in New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never boarded a plane alone in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to escort me to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought. We managed to get into Yoshida Productions and NHN.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa's infiltration was a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, getting into NHN is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this, they won't suspect a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As her manager, Mogi-san will be able to get in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely want someone to be able to go in and out freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll be watching Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Near. {\alpha&HFF&}Let me speak to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Near. Let me speak to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. {\alpha&HFF&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to capture Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}I have come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to capture Kira, I have come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan? {\alpha&HFF&}Why did he tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan? Why did he tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L. {\alpha&HFF&}You should be watching Takada-san to aid your investigation on Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L. You should be watching Takada-san to aid your investigation on Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}I am currently in contact with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I am currently in contact with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to catch Kira, keeping an eye on NHN and Takada Kiyomi is common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please inform Takada that some members from the SPK has come to Japan to capture Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bait for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I would like her to know this as well;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The SPK has only four members, myself included.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will certainly try to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we will get him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Get him instead", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in Japan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we are pretty close to each other. {\alpha&HFF&}We could even meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we are pretty close to each other. We could even meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, I'll count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the time we settle this Kira matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, since that time, this has been a one-on-one fight with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of going against L, I am going against L's successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going for it, I am going for it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet, we'll see who is better...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is at the higher position...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, this fight will come to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will stand on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's revise what we have so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}We'll call him L-Kira for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is Kira. We'll call him L-Kira for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the other, {\alpha&HFF&}the one who is holding the notebook, and doing the killing, X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the other, the one who is holding the notebook, and doing the killing, {\alpha&HFF&}X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the other, the one who is holding the notebook, and doing the killing, X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira is doing the judgments, {\alpha&HFF&}and definitely has the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira is doing the judgments, and definitely has the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, L-Kira and X-Kira are using Takada as a bridge to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the actual method to beat Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}there are two ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the actual method to beat Kira, there are two ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first way will be to... {\alpha&HFF&}kill both L-Kira and X-Kira, and take the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first way will be to... kill both L-Kira and X-Kira, and take the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}we will never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we will never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the way we work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing someone to see if the judgments will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of trial and error is not L's, nor my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L would not accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be meaningless as the successor to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, I heard on the news that you're receiving countless fan letters daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It seems there are at least 200 of them each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200 of them? I'm getting jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listening to them without any pictures is pretty boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think fan letters are something you should just skip through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read the messages from now on in a calm manner so that people listening to this won't notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the SPK on the move, {\alpha&HFF&}right now, for your own safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the SPK on the move, right now, for your own safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of just waiting for his messages, {\alpha&HFF&}you should go and tell him about your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of just waiting for his messages, you should go and tell him about your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light is making his move right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should not be just the spokesperson for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try to call out Kira from your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T has other missions: {\alpha&HFF&}creating a perfect world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T has other missions: creating a perfect world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to have you carrying out the judgment of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, so I'm sure you can do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing that, information that you don't want the SPK to know can be passed on to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Light-kun for you! He's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate. {\alpha&HFF&}Eliminate. Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate. Eliminate. {\alpha&HFF&}Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate. Eliminate. Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send a fan letter than only I will recognize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, {\alpha&HFF&}include five pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, include five pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I receive it, carry on with your judgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after I send it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not use the real notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}but carry out your judgments with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not use the real notebook, but carry out your judgments with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a fake one that looks like the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And use that for your judgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... {\alpha&HFF&}what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is no need for me to think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will just carry out God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this program?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the program that replaced "Kira's Realm".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up with something like this is just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Today's Miss Takada, we will introduce the four bodyguards of Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the 22nd World Female Karate Championships, Oyama Tatsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former CIA investigator, Hal Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a SPK member among them, this Hal Lidner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Near didn't make any effort to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.61,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Shinjuku business district, six people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to choose X-Kira, who would I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:42.91,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's existence, as well as Kira's teachings, are to be considered good, and should be infused into the minds of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada was chosen because she is a supporter of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira must have known that she is a supporter of Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}A person that has a certain relationship with Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira must have known that she is a supporter of Kira. A person that has a certain relationship with Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will not allow any criminal acts, no matter how small they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, targets for his judgments will include all the humans in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely want to hear Kira's voice and thoughts one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that Kira's teaching is the straightest path to world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young people with talent should not be allowed to waste them. They should use their talents to improve society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't have instructions or directions from Kira, I think it's necessary for us to make our own judgments based on Kira's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Kira is Yagami Light. {\alpha&HFF&}Could X-Kira be Mikami Teru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Kira is Yagami Light. Could X-Kira be Mikami Teru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is making sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ask, why am I not the main attraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they said I'm the highlight of this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, highlight is highlight. The main attraction is something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, you have to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot. She doesn't know she's just being used by Light in his investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! If you go on, you might get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. That's why I am saying this softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! {\alpha&HFF&}She smirked at me! Misa is going to break her legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! She smirked at me! {\alpha&HFF&}Misa is going to break her legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! She smirked at me! Misa is going to break her legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! {\alpha&HFF&}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What?"... I was just going to ask the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidner. She is my important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be too hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Takada-sama. I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... {\alpha&HFF&}Misa-Misa! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Misa-Misa! {\alpha&HFF&}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Misa-Misa! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}if mister Aizawa is there, is it possible for me to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if mister Aizawa is there, {\alpha&HFF&}is it possible for me to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if mister Aizawa is there, is it possible for me to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, this is Aizawa. {\alpha&HFF&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, this is Aizawa. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When L meets Takada, {\alpha&HFF&}are there cameras and bugs used to record their conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When L meets Takada, are there cameras and bugs used to record their conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}Right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they only use bugs, it's possible that X-Kira and L-Kira are communicating through Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means, Lidner is in a pretty dangerous situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put things bluntly, the most important thing right now is to let L focus on Takada and Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have to use this chance to get Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Gevanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it's amazingly simple to trail him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not hiding or anything, and he has lived in the same room for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he seems to be leading a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing his prosecution job normally as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he is X-Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is an extremely high possibility that Mikami is X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pay more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch him carefully until he goes back to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... don't make me do this again and again, NHN...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:15:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was only told "Please pay attention to what you say" again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will ask her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa, Takada wanted to have dinner with you and talk girl-to-girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kiyomi... what is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that be great? The show's host and highlight having dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, the dinner is confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's something I'm looking forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidner, make sure we get a respectable room, and sit in with us for the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san. Sorry for making you come at this late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really leave until I'm done with News 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Misa is actually quite fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What?"? I really don't know how to answer your sudden question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be very busy these days. Do you manage to see him nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm seeing him. He's still just like a boy in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every night when he comes home, he's very sticky to me. It's very troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you are getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would like to let you know something in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to announce my engagement with him at the New Year Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! You can't possibly get engaged with just one person consenting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a month since we agreed on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be okay for me to announce that in the show, host?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it can be done that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to use your authority as the host to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could you possibly... {\alpha&HFF&}try to get Kira to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could you possibly... try to get Kira to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. {\alpha&HFF&}Kira decides who he wants to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Kira decides who he wants to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you as a friend. {\alpha&HFF&}Please don't say something as cold as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you as a friend. Please don't say something as cold as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter how bad a person it is, I don't kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine. Although I like Kira, he's soon going to be caught by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's caught, you'll get your share too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will definitely be... {\alpha&HFF&}put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will definitely be... put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama! {\alpha&HFF&}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you will be with me, as the goddess of the new world.
