Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Neither am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can have dinner when you are a bit older and have more manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, I'm older than you, Kiyomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to leave a table before the dinner ends, that's even worse manners, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochii!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an easy victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In tonight's meeting between Takada and Amane, their conversation was about "him".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, who is the real girlfriend of Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this, what I can say is...
